Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.49,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,呐 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:44.21,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,突然發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:47.54,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,大概 我已經喜歡上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.03,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,微不足道 小心翼翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:53.97,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,多愁善感的 我的戀心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:06.16,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,想要見你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:13.06,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,不知何時起 氾濫成災
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:18.15,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,害怕受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:23.25,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,故意對你冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:28.39,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,但其實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:32.74,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,是希望你能夠注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:38.96,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,膽小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.51,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,呐 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.28,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,突然發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:46.71,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,大概 我已經喜歡上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:50.01,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,想要告訴你我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:53.91,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,但我的多愁善感 是個阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.40,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,呐 吻我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:57.11,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,不要離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:00.49,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,如果能說得出口的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.87,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,會不會見到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:08.83,town_OP_CN,,0,0,0,,我所不知道的你
